sub_questions: Filter records where Committee is Environmental Matters
Extract First Elected years from filtered records
Calculate average of First Elected years

scale_issues: District column contains mixed formats (decimal notation like '05.2 5B' and integers like '11')

format_notes: District column has mixed formats with some entries containing decimal notation and sub-district labels
Committee column contains full committee names, some with additional roles in parentheses like '(Vice-Chair)'
First Elected column contains year values as strings

constraints: First Elected must be convertible to numeric year
Committee field must contain the exact phrase 'Environmental Matters'
derived_filters: Committee string matching should handle variations like 'Environmental Matters (Vice-Chair)'
output_format_requirements: Result should be a single numeric value representing the average year
Average should be calculated only from valid year values
